<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="post-n">post <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /pəʊst/    美 /poʊst/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-position">1.★ <strong>职位；要职 (position)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a full-time post 
全职岗位</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He <strong>holds an</strong> important <strong>post</strong> in the company. 
他在公司担任要职。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>(军警的) 岗位：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The policeman was still <strong>at his post</strong> at dawn. 
直到黎明时分，那个警察依然坚守岗位。</p></div></div>